    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん？\nなにボーッとしてるんですか？",
      "startTime": 18.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、ごめんごめん\nじゃあ、サンドイッチにしておこうかな……",
      "startTime": 22.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3633.3333333000014,
          "startTime": 26.3
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12599.999999999998,
          "startTime": 35.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "サンドイッチ……と。送信しておきました\nちょっとお手洗い行ってきます",
      "startTime": 32.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（……仕事終わりの昼食が、まさかのファミレスか）\n（いつもだったら、好物をねだってくるのに……）",
      "startTime": 40.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4566.6666666999945,
          "startTime": 44.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "……またボーッとしてますよ\nそんな調子で大丈夫ですか？　この後の会食",
      "startTime": 48.3216653392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、そんなに気になるんです？\n私がファミレスを選んだこと",
      "startTime": 55.9570376036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……正直に言うと、な\n怜は、身バレするかもって心配にならないのか？",
      "startTime": 61.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "はい、別に。ちゃんと変装もしてますし\nむしろ、案外バレないものなんだな、って",
      "startTime": 70.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "サングラス掛けてるだけなのに……\nふふっ。これは、一つ収穫です",
      "startTime": 77.5666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（まるで、変装の予行演習みたいな言い方だ）\n（変装しなくちゃいけない予定があるってことか）",
      "startTime": 85.7666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（やっぱり芽衣の言ってた、地下で行われる）\n（秘密のライブバトルに出場するつもりなんだな）",
      "startTime": 92.1666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "……そしたら、さくらが急に……\nって、聞いてます？",
      "startTime": 99.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "もう、本当にどうしたんですか？\nずっと心ここにあらずで",
      "startTime": 104.8102014761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "大事な仕事の報告をしてるんですから\nちゃんと聞いてて下さいよ",
      "startTime": 110.4000050863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "……むしろ、何か悩んでるなら、話して下さい\n一人でボーッとされるより有意義ですから",
      "startTime": 117.0000096639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あぁ。ごめん。その……\n怜は、『アイドル地下闘技場』……って知ってるか？",
      "startTime": 123.4000096639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "…………っ！？\n……な、なんですか、それ？",
      "startTime": 131.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんかいかにも、アングラな名前ですね\nそれが……何か？",
      "startTime": 139.6000076294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いや、風の噂で存在を知ってな\n俺の周りでも、参加してる人がいるとかいないとか",
      "startTime": 145.2550143004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "へ……へぇ～……\nわ、私は関係ない……ですよ？　うん……",
      "startTime": 153.3000076294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "あっ！　お、オムライス来た～\nお、美味しそうだなぁ、あはは～！",
      "startTime": 162.7542405352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（怪し過ぎる……確定だな）",
      "startTime": 168.2379621504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_01-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "ごちそうさまでした、{user}さん\nそれにしても……タクシーなかなか捕まりませんね",
      "startTime": 176.7000045776,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-01.m4a",
